verses.text: And it came to pass after the plague , that the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* spake unto Moses and unto Eleazar the son of Aaron the priest , saying ,
Take the sum of all the congregation of the children of Israel , from twenty years old and upward , throughout their fathers’ house , all that are able to go to war in Israel.
And Moses and Eleazar the priest spake with them in the plains of Moab by Jordan \add near\add* Jericho , saying ,

\add Take the sum of the people\add*, from twenty years old and upward ; as the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* commanded Moses and the children of Israel , which went forth out of the land of Egypt. \p
¶ Reuben , the eldest son of Israel : the children of Reuben ; Hanoch , \add of whom cometh\add* the family of the Hanochites : of Pallu , the family of the Palluites :
Of Hezron , the family of the Hezronites : of Carmi , the family of the Carmites.
These \add are\add* the families of the Reubenites : and they that were numbered of them were forty and three thousand and seven hundred and thirty.
And the sons of Pallu ; Eliab.

And the sons of Eliab ; Nemuel , and Dathan , and Abiram. This \add is that\add* Dathan and Abiram , \add which were\add* famous in the congregation , who strove against Moses and against Aaron in the company of Korah , when they strove against the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*:
And the earth opened her mouth , and swallowed them up together with Korah , when that company died , what time the fire devoured two hundred and fifty men : and they became a sign.
Notwithstanding the children of Korah died not. \p

¶ The sons of Simeon after their families : of Nemuel , the family of the Nemuelites : of Jamin , the family of the Jaminites : of Jachin , the family of the Jachinites :\f + \fr 26.12 \ft Nemuel: also called, Jemuel\f*\f + \fr 26.12 \ft Jachin: also called, Jarib\f*
Of Zerah , the family of the Zarhites : of Shaul , the family of the Shaulites.\f + \fr 26.13 \ft Zerah: also called, Zohar\f*
These \add are\add* the families of the Simeonites , twenty and two thousand and two hundred. \p

¶ The children of Gad after their families : of Zephon , the family of the Zephonites : of Haggi , the family of the Haggites : of Shuni , the family of the Shunites :\f + \fr 26.15 \ft Zephon: also called, Ziphion\f*
Of Ozni , the family of the Oznites : of Eri , the family of the Erites :\f + \fr 26.16 \ft Ozni: also called, Ezbon\f*
Of Arod , the family of the Arodites : of Areli , the family of the Arelites.\f + \fr 26.17 \ft Arod: also called, Arodi\f*
These \add are\add* the families of the children of Gad according to those that were numbered of them, forty thousand and five hundred. \p
¶ The sons of Judah \add were\add* Er and Onan : and Er and Onan died in the land of Canaan.
And the sons of Judah after their families were; of Shelah , the family of the Shelanites : of Pharez , the family of the Pharzites : of Zerah , the family of the Zarhites.
And the sons of Pharez were; of Hezron , the family of the Hezronites : of Hamul , the family of the Hamulites.
These \add are\add* the families of Judah according to those that were numbered of them, threescore and sixteen thousand and five hundred. \p
¶ \add Of\add* the sons of Issachar after their families : \add of\add* Tola , the family of the Tolaites : of Pua , the family of the Punites :\f + \fr 26.23 \ft Pua: or, Phuvah\f*
Of Jashub , the family of the Jashubites : of Shimron , the family of the Shimronites.\f + \fr 26.24 \ft Jashub: or, Job\f*
These \add are\add* the families of Issachar according to those that were numbered of them, threescore and four thousand and three hundred. \p
¶ \add Of\add* the sons of Zebulun after their families : of Sered , the family of the Sardites : of Elon , the family of the Elonites : of Jahleel , the family of the Jahleelites.
These \add are\add* the families of the Zebulunites according to those that were numbered of them, threescore thousand and five hundred. \p
¶ The sons of Joseph after their families \add were\add* Manasseh and Ephraim.
Of the sons of Manasseh : of Machir , the family of the Machirites : and Machir begat Gilead : of Gilead \add come\add* the family of the Gileadites.
These \add are\add* the sons of Gilead : \add of\add* Jeezer , the family of the Jeezerites : of Helek , the family of the Helekites :\f + \fr 26.30 \ft Jeezer: also called Abiezer\f*
And \add of\add* Asriel , the family of the Asrielites : and \add of\add* Shechem , the family of the Shechemites :
And \add of\add* Shemida , the family of the Shemidaites : and \add of\add* Hepher , the family of the Hepherites. \p
¶ And Zelophehad the son of Hepher had no sons , but daughters : and the names of the daughters of Zelophehad \add were\add* Mahlah , and Noah , Hoglah , Milcah , and Tirzah.
These \add are\add* the families of Manasseh , and those that were numbered of them, fifty and two thousand and seven hundred. \p

¶ These \add are\add* the sons of Ephraim after their families : of Shuthelah , the family of the Shuthalhites : of Becher , the family of the Bachrites : of Tahan , the family of the Tahanites.\f + \fr 26.35 \ft Becher: also called, Bered\f*
And these \add are\add* the sons of Shuthelah : of Eran , the family of the Eranites.

These \add are\add* the families of the sons of Ephraim according to those that were numbered of them, thirty and two thousand and five hundred. These \add are\add* the sons of Joseph after their families. \p

¶ The sons of Benjamin after their families : of Bela , the family of the Belaites : of Ashbel , the family of the Ashbelites : of Ahiram , the family of the Ahiramites :\f + \fr 26.38 \ft Ahiram: also called, Ehi, or, Aharah\f*
Of Shupham , the family of the Shuphamites : of Hupham , the family of the Huphamites.\f + \fr 26.39 \ft Shupham…Hupham: also called, Muppim and Huppim\f*
And the sons of Bela were Ard and Naaman : \add of Ard\add*, the family of the Ardites : \add and\add* of Naaman , the family of the Naamites.\f + \fr 26.40 \ft Ard: also called, Addar\f*
These \add are\add* the sons of Benjamin after their families : and they that were numbered of them \add were\add* forty and five thousand and six hundred. \p

¶ These \add are\add* the sons of Dan after their families : of Shuham , the family of the Shuhamites. These \add are\add* the families of Dan after their families.\f + \fr 26.42 \ft Shuham: or, Hushim\f*
All the families of the Shuhamites , according to those that were numbered of them, \add were\add* threescore and four thousand and four hundred. \p
¶ \add Of\add* the children of Asher after their families : of Jimna , the family of the Jimnites : of Jesui , the family of the Jesuites : of Beriah , the family of the Beriites.
Of the sons of Beriah : of Heber , the family of the Heberites : of Malchiel , the family of the Malchielites.
And the name of the daughter of Asher \add was\add* Sarah.
These \add are\add* the families of the sons of Asher according to those that were numbered of them; \add who were\add* fifty and three thousand and four hundred. \p
¶ \add Of\add* the sons of Naphtali after their families : of Jahzeel , the family of the Jahzeelites : of Guni , the family of the Gunites :
Of Jezer , the family of the Jezerites : of Shillem , the family of the Shillemites.\f + \fr 26.49 \ft Shillem: also called, Shallum\f*
These \add are\add* the families of Naphtali according to their families : and they that were numbered of them \add were\add* forty and five thousand and four hundred.
These \add were\add* the numbered of the children of Israel , six hundred thousand and a thousand seven hundred and thirty. \p
¶ And the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* spake unto Moses , saying ,
Unto these the land shall be divided for an inheritance according to the number of names.

To many thou shalt give the more inheritance , and to few thou shalt give the less inheritance : to every one shall his inheritance be given according to those that were numbered of him.\f + \fr 26.54 \ft give the more…: Heb. multiply his inheritance\f*\f + \fr 26.54 \ft give the less…: Heb. diminish his inheritance\f*
Notwithstanding the land shall be divided by lot : according to the names of the tribes of their fathers they shall inherit.
According to the lot shall the possession thereof be divided between many and few. \p

¶ And these \add are\add* they that were numbered of the Levites after their families : of Gershon , the family of the Gershonites : of Kohath , the family of the Kohathites : of Merari , the family of the Merarites.

These \add are\add* the families of the Levites : the family of the Libnites , the family of the Hebronites , the family of the Mahlites , the family of the Mushites , the family of the Korathites. And Kohath begat Amram.
And the name of Amram’s wife \add was\add* Jochebed , the daughter of Levi , whom \add her mother\add* bare to Levi in Egypt : and she bare unto Amram Aaron and Moses , and Miriam their sister.
And unto Aaron was born Nadab , and Abihu , Eleazar , and Ithamar.
And Nadab and Abihu died , when they offered strange fire before the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*.

And those that were numbered of them were twenty and three thousand , all males from a month old and upward : for they were not numbered among the children of Israel , because there was no inheritance given them among the children of Israel. \p
¶ These \add are\add* they that were numbered by Moses and Eleazar the priest , who numbered the children of Israel in the plains of Moab by Jordan \add near\add* Jericho.
But among these there was not a man of them whom Moses and Aaron the priest numbered , when they numbered the children of Israel in the wilderness of Sinai.

For the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* had said of them, They shall surely die in the wilderness. And there was not left a man of them, save Caleb the son of Jephunneh , and Joshua the son of Nun.
